                    <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Privacy Policy for Maqao Plus Rental Management System</h2>
                    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> August 8, 2024</p>

                    <h3>1. Introduction</h3>
                    <p>Welcome to Maqao Plus, a rental management system designed to streamline property management, payment processing, and tenant interaction. We prioritize your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data in accordance with Kenyan data protection laws. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our application.</p>

                    <h3>2. Information We Collect</h3>
                    <p><strong>Personal Information:</strong> We may collect personal details that you provide directly, including:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Your name, email address, and phone number.</li>
                        <li><strong>Property Details:</strong> Information about the properties you manage or rent, including addresses and lease details.</li>
                        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Details of transactions, payment methods, and billing history.</li>
                        <li><strong>Maintenance Requests:</strong> Information about maintenance issues reported by tenants.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We also gather data on how you use our app, such as:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>App Usage:</strong> Features used, pages visited, and session duration.</li>
                        <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
                    <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Provide Services:</strong> Manage and process property listings, payments, and maintenance requests.</li>
                        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Send updates, notifications, and respond to your inquiries.</li>
                        <li><strong>Improve Our Services:</strong> Analyze app usage to enhance functionality and performance.</li>
                        <li><strong>Compliance:</strong> Meet legal obligations and enforce our terms and conditions.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>4. Data Protection</h3>
                    <p>We are committed to ensuring the security of your personal data:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> Data is encrypted during transmission and storage.</li>
                        <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Restricted access to personal data to authorized personnel.</li>
                        <li><strong>Regular Reviews:</strong> Periodic security assessments to address potential vulnerabilities.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>5. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h3>
                    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal data. We may share your information in the following situations:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With partners who assist us in delivering services, under confidentiality agreements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by Kenyan law, or to protect our rights and those of our users.</li>
                        <li><strong>Business Transactions:</strong> In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, where data may be transferred as part of the transaction.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h3>6. Your Rights and Choices</h3>
                    <p>Under the Data Protection Act, 2019, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request access to your personal data.</li>
                        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Request correction of inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
                        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your data when it is no longer necessary.</li>
                        <li><strong>Objection:</strong> Object to processing based on legitimate interests.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us using the details provided below.</p>

                    <h3>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date. Your continued use of our app after changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

                    <h3>8. Contact Us</h3>
